Package: drg
Type: Package
Title: DS1-Lab2-Group5 R Package
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Hanyu Liu, Haotian Liu, Jiayue Cheng
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: This package contains two functions. drg_to_payment is a function that makes a boxplot of payments by DRG code. User has the option to choose to see either the average Medicare payments, the average total payment, or the average covered charges by entering "Medicare", "Total", "Covered" as input, respectively. 
    drg_statistics is a function that calculates statistics over all of the DRG codes for average Medicare payments. User has the option to calculate either the mean, median or standard deviation of the DRG codes by entering mean, median, "standard deviation", respectively.
Depends:
    tidyverse
